      "comment" : "Wide canvas – wallpaper prompt"
    },
    "Set today's energy canvas as your Lock Screen wallpaper automatically each time you close the app." : {

    },
    "Set up the wallpaper shortcut first" : {

    },
    "Settings" : {
      "comment" : "Context menu action\nSettings page title\nTab bar title"
    },
    "SETUP" : {
      "comment" : "Wallpaper section header"
    },
    "Share canvas" : {
      "comment" : "GalleryView – share button VoiceOver label"
    },
    "ShieldAction Logs" : {

    },
    "Sign in" : {
      "comment" : "Onboarding – Apple sign-in button label"
    },
    "Sign in with Apple" : {

    },
    "Signed in" : {
      "comment" : "Onboarding – Apple sign-in success state"
    },
    "Skip" : {

    },
    "skip all" : {

    },
    "Sleep" : {
      "comment" : "StepBalanceCard – sleep chip label"
    },
    "sleep and" : {

    },
    "sleep data may lag a bit — ios updates it on its own schedule." : {

    },
    "sleep deepens the dark." : {

    },
    "Sleep Goal" : {

    },
    "Sleep hours" : {

    },
    "Sleep is what we all have. This is the beginning and the end of the day. And its amount and quality influence us the most. On the canvas the more you sleep, the darker it becomes. That's not a bad thing, it just shows that rest today is a priority. Oh, btw, it is taken from the Health app and sometimes it is slow to upload. Thanks, Apple." : {
      "comment" : "Note body"
    },
    "Sleep only" : {
      "comment" : "GradientPreview – preview mode sleep data only"
    },
    "sleep." : {

    },
    "Sleeping for 8 hours or making 10k steps a day is not a must. It's personal, you set your own threshold. But setting it gives a bit more motivation to get there." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_limits"
    },
    "Slide %lld of %lld" : {
      "comment" : "Onboarding – progress bar VoiceOver value",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Slide %1$lld of %2$lld"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "so i made this app." : {

    },
    "Solid" : {
      "comment" : "Widget background style"
    },
    "Some permissions are missing" : {
      "comment" : "Permissions – missing banner title"
    },
    "someone" : {

    },
    "Something went wrong" : {

    },
    "spend" : {

    },
    "spend colors" : {
      "comment" : "PayGate title"
    },
    "Spend colors on" : {
      "comment" : "Unlock section header"
    },
    "spend them on the apps that pull you away." : {

    },
    "Spent" : {

    },
    "Stay present, control screen time" : {

    },
    "steps" : {
      "comment" : "Onboarding – steps unit label"
    },
    "Steps" : {
      "comment" : "StepBalanceCard – steps chip label"
    },
    "steps a day." : {

    },
    "Steps and sleep come from the Health app and are the same for everyone. Body, mind and heart are activities you add by tapping the + button at the bottom of the screen." : {

    },
    "Steps are not a fitness metric. They're proof the body moved through the world. The more you walk, the brighter the canvas becomes." : {
      "comment" : "Note body: about_steps"
    },
    "Steps balance" : {
      "comment" : "StepBalanceCard – progress bar VoiceOver label"
    },
    "steps brighten it." : {

    },
    "Steps only" : {
      "comment" : "GradientPreview – preview mode steps data only"
    },
    "steps today" : {

    },
    "Steps today:" : {
      "comment" : "QuickStatus – steps label"
    },
    "Steps, sleep, workouts" : {
      "comment" : "Permission row – HealthKit detail"
    },
    "STYLE" : {
      "comment" : "Appearance section header"
    },
    "Sunset" : {

    },
    "Synced with wallpaper shortcut" : {

    },
    "tap each to see." : {

    },
    "Tap the button below to add the wallpaper shortcut" : {

    },
    "Tap to add to your daily total" : {

    },
    "Target: %@ steps" : {

    },
    "Target: %@h" : {

    },
    "Telegram" : {

    },
    "Templates" : {
      "comment" : "TemplatePicker – section header"
    },
    "Test notification." : {
      "comment" : "Notification – test notification body"
    },
    "the app needs access to apple health." : {

    },
    "The canvas is a reflection of each day. How full and colorful it was. I like the idea that even though each day is limited by 24 hours, there are so many little things that make them different. And to distinguish one day from another we need to notice them." : {
      "comment" : "Note body"
    },
    "The sense of being present" : {
      "comment" : "App tagline"
    },
    "the time runs only when the app is being used." : {

    },
    "THEME" : {
      "comment" : "Appearance section header"
    },
    "they're needed to unlock the apps." : {

    },
    "Thinking about the body, mind and heart, I was looking for the best objects to represent them on the canvas. The body is represented by big constant breathing shapes. For the mind I chose drifting circles, that fly around like ideas. And the heart is represented by beams of light, that light the way and look around." : {
      "comment" : "Note body"
    },
    "This name will be displayed instead of my real name" : {
      "comment" : "ProfileEditor – nickname hint"
    },
    "this uses apple's screen time. you'll see a system prompt." : {

